<h1 id="toc0"><span>THE CONTEST IS OVER!</span></h1>
<p>Congratulations to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5231418); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5231418&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595863926" alt="Popsioak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5231418)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5231418); return false;">Popsioak</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5549954); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595863926" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5549954); return false;">Dyslexion</a></span> for their winning entry: <a href="/scp-5250">SCP-5250</a> - &quot;Act I: The Lake South, The Deer North&quot; !</p>
<p>And of course, a huge thank-you to everyone who participated, from those who submitted containment procedures to all the pinch-hitters who contributed!</p>
